            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Welcome, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I'm helping at the grocery store, so I'm here to take an order!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You're helping at the grocery store...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Were you... Having that much trouble...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "It seems your income from your atelier is worse than I expected... Is that why you're working at the grocery store?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "N-no, that's wrong! That's not it at all!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I was wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I'm just helping because Oskar asked me for a favor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I see. I apologize for jumping to conclusions so quickly."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "But Oskar's seriously pretty terrible sometimes. He just forced his work onto me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Heh heh, you might say that, but you're still helping him. That's one of your best qualities, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Well... He's my friend, after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, you wanted an order for vegetables, correct?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I got it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Thank you."
